{"tid":998741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友想去Grad Trip","createTime":"2019-01-28T07:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T08:32:03.000Z","uid":37679,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e2adfa7428aaff1c4582e729c32a4337cbd90e5e","tid":998741,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"小弟同女朋友今年都Final Year<br />\n咁由於我地兩個開sem完sem都唔同<br />\n我啱啱完sem佢就話係佢搵工期<br />\n所以就唔到時間一齊去Grad Trip<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁呢兩個星期就Reg科 因為year 4早Reg<br />\n我就去問下佢咁reg好唔好<br />\n點reg好唔好 諗住就到時間sem中間走堂同佢去<br />\n跟住又係咁話我好煩 又話驚我炒<br />\n大學讀左咁耐 啲堂上定唔上大家心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔小心打左句野叫佢<br />\n一係同fd子去 一係就等我6月完sem先去<br />\n打完先記起佢啲中同無緣無故走哂Gp拋棄左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班八婆Lm佢地成世都俾狗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAnyway 而家個情況就係咁<br />\n其實同佢一齊既時候 啲timetable成日都已經夾唔到<br />\n有冇其他巴打有過差唔多情況可以過兩招俾我"},{"pid":"d106602bcced6eb759625953eb1c1a5a4482691c","tid":998741,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"點解都條女去啦 任中出 口爆"},{"pid":"19738771dfae927762c92384ca248468690369ed","tid":998741,"uid":210161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"Grad trip 係同fd既同學去<br />\n都唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd2d2c6e4f67deec768e4a1e39e9ac40707238d","tid":998741,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:58:56.000Z","msg":"我啱啱完sem佢就話係佢搵工期<br />\n所以就唔到時間一齊去Grad Trip<br />\n<br />\n條女寧願搵工都唔撚同你去 心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c82bf3e701229bd59322bd6369f129fcbacf69","tid":998741,"uid":210161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-